      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "STOCKTON, Cal, Oct. 4.-\"The\nplace for you women is the home,\nwhere you belong. AS long as I am\nin the governoy's chair of Califor-\nmia. woman's suffrage bill never\nshall became law. Governor\nJames n. Gillett.\n\n\n\"Why, governor, what do you\nmean? Don't you remember the\ntime when you came unsolicited to\nthe Santa Cruz convention, which\ngave you the nomination. and\npledged yourself to our cause ~\nLillian Harris Coffin."
    }
